species.name: fezandipiti
descriptions: Fezandipiti beats its glossy wings to scatter pheromones that captivate people and Pokémon.
Fezandipiti owes its beautiful looks and lovely voice to the toxic stimulants emanating from the chain wrapped around its body.

abilities.name: technician
abilities.effect: Strengthens moves of 60 base power or less to 1.5× their power.
